{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">NDE Near Dungeon Experience - A retro SNES styled turn-based RPG/Survival game.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore 7 Dungeons, as you ascend upwards towards the truth of where you are and who you are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reclaim your memories, fight or avoid enemies, solve puzzles, collect treasure, trade with and be Guided by... Guide, a mysterious spirit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn skills  and figure out what strategies work best for each enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find tools to access new areas of each dungeon, you can climb, dig, jump, light your way and find previously inaccessible areas...and an Easter Egg or two.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With the SIN SYSTEM your stats are altered according to your choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Also, being an SNES inspired game, there are NO AUTO-Saves, so save save save.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ADDITIONAL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are 4 modes of gameplay; Fighter (EASY), Loner (NORMAL), Scholar (HARD) and Ecto (NIGHTMARE)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each with their own gears, shops, enemies and skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A playthrough of ALL MODES is approximately 11 Hours... for me...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utilizes RPG Maker VX Ace, so naturally the focus was to create a game as NON-Vanilla as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All the Music and graphics are original.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249890/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729593517","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249890/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729593517","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249890/b9e88297549bc8cae368245eb9e3acc3b1566aeb/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729593517","ca